tweet: I think @shaine wanted to sleep late this morning but the baby is jumping up and down on the bed and making tons of noise.
She wished me a "Happy Thanksgiving" anyway.
Some chick just sent me a text thinking it was a friend of hers. She didn't get upset when I told her I didn't know her.
There should be a way to block unwanted text messages to my phone.
I can hear the baby's awake. Going to ignore her while I clean up here so she can make more mess in the living room.
